# Git 行尾符配置
# 统一使用 LF（Unix 风格），避免 Windows CRLF 警告

* text=auto eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.txt text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.csv text eol=lf

# 二进制文件
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.pdf binary
*.pth binary
*.txt binary
*.log binary


